thread.title: MICHAEL
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by MICHAEL

author: MICHAEL
title: MICHAEL
text: The Holden provided was a lovely surprise, ran well and was well presented. The only comment I could suggest would be a larger a more permanent looking reception/waiting area. While waiting my turn to be served, it was very stuffy and cramped in the cabin Redspot are currently operating out of there in the city. However, I will be using this company again - MC
